@startuml state_room
title Room State-Chart
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor      #E2EFDA
  BorderColor          #1F3864
  ArrowColor           #1F3864
  FontColor            #1F3864
  StartColor           #1F3864
  EndColor             #1F3864
}

[*] --> available
state available : unoccupied and ready
state occupied : assigned to active reservation

available --> occupied : allocate() [FR-4.2]
occupied --> available : checkOut() [FR-6.6]
@enduml